table.name: vtiger_rsnaborevues
table.sql: CREATE TABLE `vtiger_rsnaborevues` ( `rsnaborevuesid` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `isabonne` VARCHAR(5) DEFAULT NULL, `debutabo` DATE DEFAULT NULL, `finabo` DATE DEFAULT NULL, `rsnabotype` VARCHAR(128) DEFAULT NULL, `accountid` INT(11) DEFAULT NULL, `nbexemplaires` INT(11) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`rsnaborevuesid`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8
